---
// Bento grid features section
---

<section class="bento" id="features">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header reveal">
      <span class="section-header__tag">Built for Pakistan</span>
      <h2 class="section-header__title">Healthcare That Speaks Your Language</h2>
      <p class="section-header__desc">A two-pronged platform: AI-powered patient chat and a professional doctor dashboard — designed for how 220 million Pakistanis actually access care.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="bento__grid">
      <div class="bento__card bento__card--wide reveal">
        <div class="bento__card-content">
          <span class="bento__card-tag">Multilingual</span>
          <h3 class="bento__card-title">Chat in Your Language</h3>
          <p class="bento__card-desc">Chat in Urdu, English, Roman Urdu, or any language you prefer. Full RTL and Nastaliq support for Urdu speakers, plus voice messages — our AI understands you naturally.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bento__card-visual bento__card-visual--lang">
          <div class="bento__chat-bubble bento__chat-bubble--urdu">Mujhe sar mein dard hai aur bukhar bhi hai</div>
          <div class="bento__chat-bubble bento__chat-bubble--ai">Main samajh gaya. Kuch sawalat poochta hoon taake aapki haalat ka andaaza ho sake...</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bento__card reveal reveal--delay-1">
        <div class="bento__card-icon bento__card-icon--blue">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 1a3 3 0 0 0-3 3v8a3 3 0 0 0 6 0V4a3 3 0 0 0-3-3z"/><path d="M19 10v2a7 7 0 0 1-14 0v-2"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="bento__card-title">Guided Symptom Collection</h3>
        <p class="bento__card-desc">Our AI asks structured follow-up questions to build a complete picture — just like a real doctor's consultation, averaging 3-7 messages per session.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bento__card reveal reveal--delay-2">
        <div class="bento__card-icon bento__card-icon--purple">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="bento__card-title">Family Profiles</h3>
        <p class="bento__card-desc">Add family members — parents, children, grandparents — each with their own medical history and consultation records under one account.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bento__card reveal">
        <div class="bento__card-icon bento__card-icon--green">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polygon points="13 2 3 14 12 14 11 22 21 10 12 10 13 2"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="bento__card-title">Real-Time Notifications</h3>
        <p class="bento__card-desc">Get instant alerts when your doctor reviews your case and approves your prescription. No waiting rooms, no queues — results in minutes.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bento__card bento__card--wide reveal reveal--delay-1">
        <div class="bento__card-content">
          <span class="bento__card-tag">AI + Doctor Dashboard</span>
          <h3 class="bento__card-title">AI Triage. Doctor Verification.</h3>
          <p class="bento__card-desc">Our AI collects symptoms and generates a health assessment. A licensed doctor then reviews the full session transcript, adds their medical opinion, and approves the prescription — with their name on it.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bento__card-visual bento__card-visual--process">
          <div class="bento__process">
            <div class="bento__process-step"><div class="bento__process-icon bento__process-icon--1"><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"/></svg></div><span>Symptom Input</span></div>
            <div class="bento__process-arrow">&rarr;</div>
            <div class="bento__process-step"><div class="bento__process-icon bento__process-icon--2"><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/><line x1="8" y1="21" x2="16" y2="21"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12" y2="21"/></svg></div><span>AI Triage</span></div>
            <div class="bento__process-arrow">&rarr;</div>
            <div class="bento__process-step"><div class="bento__process-icon bento__process-icon--3"><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="8.5" cy="7" r="4"/><polyline points="17 11 19 13 23 9"/></svg></div><span>Doctor Review</span></div>
            <div class="bento__process-arrow">&rarr;</div>
            <div class="bento__process-step"><div class="bento__process-icon bento__process-icon--4"><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"/><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/></svg></div><span>Verified Rx</span></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
